briefdescription.para: Find a key in the given box.

parameterdescription.para: Starting point. The first index to be checked is its successer. So you have to check index number 0 yourself (which should be fast enough).

simplesect.para: index of the key structure that has been found our 0 otherwise.

briefdescription.para: Delete the key with the given index from the box.

parameterdescription.para: Box where the key shall be deleted.
Index of the key in box->current_keys of the key that shall be deleted.
